{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775884497590,"sessionID":"ses_2850952c0ffen3wW0K2szNbJk3","part":{"id":"prt_d7af6e758001mUU1gUdQ04sU8r","messageID":"msg_d7af6d5c5001F3ACPrcMAKRz8V","sessionID":"ses_2850952c0ffen3wW0K2szNbJk3","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_aaaeabe4e3614424baf95d93","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/design.md","limit":300,"offset":1000},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1000: \n1001: ---\n1002: \n1003: # Design: AR-035 client-go\n1004: \n1005: ## Overview\n1006: \n1007: Generated Kubernetes client library for API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`. Provides type-safe Go clients, informers, and listers for `AgentRuntime` and `CodeInterpreter` custom resources.\n1008: \n1009: ## Architecture\n1010: \n1011: ```\n1012: client-go/\n1013: ├── clientset/              # Typed clientset\n1014: │   ├── versioned/\n1015: │   │   ├── clientset.go           # Clientset, Interface\n1016: │   │   ├── scheme/                # Scheme registration\n1017: │   │   ├── typed/                 # Typed clients per API version\n1018: │   │   │   └── runtime/\n1019: │   │   │       └── v1alpha1/\n1020: │   │   │       ├── runtime_client.go      # RuntimeV1alpha1Client\n1021: │   │   │       ├── agentruntime.go        # AgentRuntimeInterface\n1022: │   │   │       ├── codeinterpreter.go     # CodeInterpreterInterface\n1023: │   │   │       └── fake/                  # Test fakes\n1024: │   │   └── fake/                  # Fake clientset\n1025: │   └── scheme/\n1026: ├── informers/              # SharedInformerFactory\n1027: │   └── externalversions/\n1028: │       ├── factory.go               # SharedInformerFactory\n1029: │       ├── generic.go               # GenericInformer\n1030: │       ├── runtime/                 # Group accessors\n1031: │       │   ├── interface.go\n1032: │       │   └── v1alpha1/\n1033: │       │       ├── interface.go\n1034: │       │       ├── agentruntime.go\n1035: │       │       └── codeinterpreter.go\n1036: │       └── internalinterfaces/      # Shared interfaces\n1037: └── listers/                # Listers (read-only cache)\n1038:     └── runtime/\n1039:         └── v1alpha1/\n1040:             ├── agentruntime.go\n1041:             ├── codeinterpreter.go\n1042:             └── expansion_generated.go\n1043: ```\n1044: \n1045: ## Data Structures\n1046: \n1047: ### Clientset (`clientset/versioned/clientset.go`)\n1048: \n1049: ```go\n1050: type Interface interface {\n1051:     Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\n1052:     RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n1053: }\n1054: \n1055: type Clientset struct {\n1056:     *discovery.DiscoveryClient\n1057:     runtimeV1alpha1 *runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Client\n1058: }\n1059: ```\n1060: \n1061: **Constructors:**\n1062: - `NewForConfig(*rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)` — creates client from kubeconfig\n1063: - `NewForConfigAndClient(*rest.Config, *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)` — with custom HTTP client\n1064: - `NewForConfigOrDie(*rest.Config) *Clientset` — panics on error\n1065: - `New(rest.Interface) *Clientset` — from existing REST interface\n1066: \n1067: ### Typed Client (`clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/`)\n1068: \n1069: ```go\n1070: type RuntimeV1alpha1Interface interface {\n1071:     RESTClient() rest.Interface\n1072:     AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeInterface\n1073:     CodeInterpreters(namespace string) CodeInterpreterInterface\n1074: }\n1075: \n1076: type AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n1077:     Create(ctx context.Context, obj *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n1078:     Update(ctx context.Context, obj *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n1079:     UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, obj *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n1080:     Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n1081:     DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.DeleteOptions, listOpts metav1.ListOptions) error\n1082:     Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n1083:     List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n1084:     Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n1085:     Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n1086: }\n1087: ```\n1088: \n1089: REST configuration:\n1090: - `GroupVersion`: `runtimev1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion`\n1091: - `APIPath`: `/apis`\n1092: - Serializer: from `clientset/versioned/scheme`\n1093: \n1094: ### Informer Factory (`informers/externalversions/factory.go`)\n1095: \n1096: ```go\n1097: type SharedInformerFactory interface {\n1098:     Start(stopCh <-chan struct{})\n1099:     Shutdown()\n1100:     WaitForCacheSync(stopCh <-chan struct{}) map[reflect.Type]bool\n1101:     InformerFor(obj runtime.Object, newFunc internalinterfaces.NewInformerFunc) cache.SharedIndexInformer\n1102:     Runtime() externalversionsruntime.Interface\n1103: }\n1104: ```\n1105: \n1106: **Options:**\n1107: - `WithCustomResyncConfig(time.Duration)` — per-informer resync period\n1108: - `WithTweakListOptions(TweakListOptionsFunc)` — modify ListOptions\n1109: - `WithNamespace(string)` — filter by namespace\n1110: - `WithTransform(transform.ObjectTransformFunc)` — transform objects before storage\n1111: \n1112: ### Lister (`listers/runtime/v1alpha1/`)\n1113: \n1114: ```go\n1115: type AgentRuntimeLister interface {\n1116:     List(selector labels.Selector) ([]*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n1117:     AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister\n1118: }\n1119: \n1120: type AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister interface {\n1121:     List(selector labels.Selector) ([]*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n1122:     Get(name string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n1123: }\n1124: ```\n1125: \n1126: ## API Contracts\n1127: \n1128: ### REST Endpoints\n1129: \n1130: | Resource | HTTP Method | Path | Operation |\n1131: |----------|-------------|------|-----------|\n1132: | `agentruntimes` | POST | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/agentruntimes` | Create |\n1133: | `agentruntimes` | GET | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/agentruntimes/{name}` | Get |\n1134: | `agentruntimes` | PUT | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/agentruntimes/{name}` | Update |\n1135: | `agentruntimes` | DELETE | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/agentruntimes/{name}` | Delete |\n1136: | `agentruntimes` | GET | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/agentruntimes` | List |\n1137: | `agentruntimes` | WATCH | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/agentruntimes?watch=true` | Watch |\n1138: | `agentruntimes/status` | PUT | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/agentruntimes/{name}/status` | UpdateStatus |\n1139: \n1140: ### Error Handling\n1141: \n1142: All client methods return standard Kubernetes API errors:\n1143: \n1144: ```go\n1145: // Common error patterns\n1146: errors.IsNotFound(err)        // 404 Not Found\n1147: errors.IsAlreadyExists(err)   // 409 Conflict\n1148: errors.IsConflict(err)        // 409 Conflict (resource version mismatch)\n1149: errors.IsInvalid(err)         // 422 Unprocessable Entity\n1150: errors.IsTimeout(err)         // 504 Gateway Timeout\n1151: errors.IsServiceUnavailable(err) // 503 Service Unavailable\n1152: ```\n1153: \n1154: **Client construction errors:**\n1155: - Invalid `rest.Config` → `*url.Error`, `*errors.StatusError`\n1156: - Missing credentials → `clientcmd.errConfigurationInvalid`\n1157: \n1158: **Informer errors:**\n1159: - ListWatch failure → propagated via `StopChannel` and error handlers\n1160: - Cache sync timeout → `WaitForCacheSync` returns `false`\n1161: \n1162: ## Testing Strategy\n1163: \n1164: ### Unit Tests\n1165: \n1166: **Location:** `client-go/**/*_test.go`\n1167: \n1168: ```go\n1169: // Example: fake client test\n1170: func TestAgentRuntimeCreate(t *testing.T) {\n1171:     cs := fake.NewSimpleClientset()\n1172:     runtime := &runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n1173:         ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"test\", Namespace: \"default\"},\n1174:     }\n1175:     created, err := cs.RuntimeV1alpha1().AgentRuntimes(\"default\").Create(\n1176:         context.TODO(), runtime, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n1177:     if err != nil {\n1178:         t.Fatal(err)\n1179:     }\n1180:     if created.Name != \"test\" {\n1181:         t.Errorf(\"expected name 'test', got %q\", created.Name)\n1182:     }\n1183: }\n1184: ```\n1185: \n1186: ### Integration Tests\n1187: \n1188: **Location:** `test/integration/client-go/`\n1189: \n1190: ```go\n1191: // Example: informer sync test\n1192: func TestInformerSync(t *testing.T) {\n1193:     config := rest.Config{ /* ... */ }\n1194:     cs := versioned.NewForConfigOrDie(config)\n1195:     factory := informers.NewSharedInformerFactory(cs, 0)\n1196:     informer := factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Informer()\n1197:     \n1198:     stopCh := make(chan struct{})\n1199:     defer close(stopCh)\n1200:     factory.Start(stopCh)\n1201:     \n1202:     synced := factory.WaitForCacheSync(stopCh)\n1203:     if !synced[reflect.TypeOf(&runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{})] {\n1204:         t.Fatal(\"informer did not sync\")\n1205:     }\n1206: }\n1207: ```\n1208: \n1209: ### Test Coverage Targets\n1210: \n1211: | Component | Coverage Target |\n1212: |-----------|-----------------|\n1213: | Clientset constructors | 100% |\n1214: | Typed client CRUD operations | 90% |\n1215: | Informer factory initialization | 85% |\n1216: | Lister operations | 85% |\n1217: | Fake clients | 80% |\n1218: \n1219: ## Code Generation\n1220: \n1221: **Trigger:** `make gen-client` → `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n1222: \n1223: **Dependencies:**\n1224: - `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1\n1225: - `--with-watch` flag enabled\n1226: - Output package: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n1227: \n1228: **Generated markers:**\n1229: ```go\n1230: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package\n1231: // +k8s:openapi-gen=true\n1232: // +k8s:defaulter-gen=TypeMeta\n1233: // +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n1234: ```\n1235: \n1236: **Regeneration checklist:**\n1237: 1. Update `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n1238: 2. Run `make gen-client`\n1239: 3. Verify generated code compiles\n1240: 4. Run unit tests\n1241: 5. Commit generated files\n1242: \n1243: ## Extension Points\n1244: \n1245: ### Client Expansion\n1246: \n1247: ```go\n1248: // clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/generated_expansion.go\n1249: type AgentRuntimeExpansion interface {\n1250:     // Add custom methods here\n1251: }\n1252: ```\n1253: \n1254: ### Lister Expansion\n1255: \n1256: ```go\n1257: // listers/runtime/v1alpha1/expansion_generated.go\n1258: type AgentRuntimeListerExpansion interface {\n1259:     // Add custom list/query methods here\n1260: }\n1261: ```\n1262: \n1263: ### Informer Customization\n1264: \n1265: ```go\n1266: // Using TweakListOptionsFunc\n1267: factory := informers.NewSharedInformerFactoryWithOptions(\n1268:     clientset,\n1269:     0,\n1270:     informers.WithTweakListOptions(func(opts *metav1.ListOptions) {\n1271:         opts.LabelSelector = \"environment=production\"\n1272:     }),\n1273: )\n1274: ```\n\n(End of file - total 1274 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"\n---\n\n# Design: AR-035 client-go\n\n## Overview\n\nGenerated Kubernetes client library for API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`. Provides type-safe Go clients, informers, and listers for `AgentRuntime` and `CodeInterpreter` custom resources.\n\n## Architecture\n\n```\nclient-go/\n├── clientset/              # Typed clientset\n│   ├── versioned/\n│   │   ├── clientset.go           # Clientset, Interface\n│   │   ├── scheme/                # Scheme registration\n│   │   ├── typed/                 # Typed clients per API version\n│   │   │   └── runtime/\n│   │   │       └── v1alpha1/","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/design.md","time":{"start":1775884497577,"end":1775884497588}}}}
