{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775884612965,"sessionID":"ses_2850952c0ffen3wW0K2szNbJk3","part":{"id":"prt_d7af7a08e0015xIi0cS3n5LXR2","messageID":"msg_d7af795ae001m3gfRnC7UtbgfD","sessionID":"ses_2850952c0ffen3wW0K2szNbJk3","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_9ec29ea5315445ca8c1d5b42","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-035/tasks.md","content":"# AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成 Tasks\n\n**Module:** client-go  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** L  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Code Generator Setup\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Verify k8s.io/code-generator dependency\n  - Check: `go.mod` contains `k8s.io/code-generator v0.34.1`\n  - Verify: Code-generator tools available via `go install`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2** Create hack/update-codegen.sh script\n  - File: `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n  - Configure: `--with-watch` flag enabled\n  - Configure: Output package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n  - Verify: Script is executable\n\n- [ ] **T1.3** Define code generation markers in types.go\n  - Add: `// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package`\n  - Add: `// +k8s:openapi-gen=true`\n  - Add: `// +k8s:defaulter-gen=TypeMeta`\n  - Add: `// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n  - Verify: All markers present in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n\n- [ ] **T1.4** Add make gen-client target\n  - Target: `gen-client` in `Makefile`\n  - Command: `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n  - Verify: `make gen-client` executes without error\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Clientset Generation\n\n- [ ] **T2.1** Generate clientset/versioned/clientset.go\n  - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/clientset.go`\n  - Interface: `Interface` with `Discovery()` and `RuntimeV1alpha1()`\n  - Struct: `Clientset` embedding `*discovery.DiscoveryClient`\n  - Verify: Clientset implements `Interface`\n\n- [ ] **T2.2** Generate clientset constructors\n  - Function: `NewForConfig(*rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)`\n  - Function: `NewForConfigAndClient(*rest.Config, *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)`\n  - Function: `NewForConfigOrDie(*rest.Config) *Clientset`\n  - Function: `New(rest.Interface) *Clientset`\n  - Verify: All constructors compile and return typed clientset\n\n- [ ] **T2.3** Generate scheme registration\n  - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go`\n  - Verify: `AddToScheme` registers runtime/v1alpha1 types\n  - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/scheme/doc.go`\n  - Verify: Scheme package documentation present\n\n- [ ] **T2.4** Generate fake clientset\n  - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/fake/clientset_generated.go`\n  - Function: `NewSimpleClientset()`\n  - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/fake/register.go`\n  - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/fake/doc.go`\n  - Verify: Fake clientset supports in-memory testing\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: Typed Client Generation (RuntimeV1alpha1)\n\n- [ ] **T3.1** Generate RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n  - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go`\n  - Interface: `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` with `RESTClient()`, `AgentRuntimes()`, `CodeInterpreters()`\n  - Struct: `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` implementing interface\n  - Verify: REST defaults configured (GroupVersion, APIPath, serializer)\n\n- [ ] **T3.2** Generate AgentRuntime typed client\n  - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n  - Interface: `AgentRuntimeInterface` with full CRUD operations:\n    - `Create(ctx, obj, opts) (*AgentRuntime, error)`\n    - `Update(ctx, obj, opts) (*AgentRuntime, error)`\n    - `UpdateStatus(ctx, obj, opts) (*AgentRuntime, error)`\n    - `Delete(ctx, name, opts) error`\n    - `DeleteCollection(ctx, opts, listOpts) error`\n    - `Get(ctx, name, opts) (*AgentRuntime, error)`\n    - `List(ctx, opts) (*AgentRuntimeList, error)`\n    - `Watch(ctx, opts) (watch.Interface, error)`\n    - `Patch(ctx, name, pt, data, opts, subresources...) (*AgentRuntime, error)`\n  - Verify: All methods compile and return correct types\n\n- [ ] **T3.3** Generate CodeInterpreter typed client\n  - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n  - Interface: `CodeInterpreterInterface` with same CRUD methods\n  - Verify: Methods use `*CodeInterpreter` and `CodeInterpreterList` types\n\n- [ ] **T3.4** Generate expansion interfaces\n  - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/generated_expansion.go`\n  - Interface: `AgentRuntimeExpansion` (empty)\n  - Interface: `CodeInterpreterExpansion` (empty)\n  - Verify: Expansion hooks available for custom methods\n\n- [ ] **T3.5** Generate fake typed clients\n  - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_runtime_client.go`\n  - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_agentruntime.go`\n  - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_codeinterpreter.go`\n  - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/doc.go`\n  - Verify: Fake clients implement typed interfaces\n\n- [ ] **T3.6** Generate doc.go files\n  - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go`\n  - Verify: Package documentation present\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: Informer Factory Generation\n\n- [ ] **T4.1** Generate SharedInformerFactory\n  - File: `client-go/informers/externalversions/factory.go`\n  - Interface: `SharedInformerFactory` with:\n    - `Start(stopCh)`\n    - `Shutdown()`\n    - `WaitForCacheSync(stopCh) map[reflect.Type]bool`\n    - `InformerFor(obj, newFunc)`\n    - `ForResource(resource) (GenericInformer, error)`\n    - `Runtime() externalversionsruntime.Interface`\n  - Verify: Factory manages informer lifecycle\n\n- [ ] **T4.2** Generate factory constructors\n  - Function: `NewSharedInformerFactory(client, defaultResync)`\n  - Function: `NewSharedInformerFactoryWithOptions(client, defaultResync, options...)`\n  - Function: `NewFilteredSharedInformerFactory` (deprecated)\n  - Options: `WithCustomResyncConfig`, `WithTweakListOptions`, `WithNamespace`, `WithTransform`\n  - Verify: All constructors compile\n\n- [ ] **T4.3** Generate group interface\n  - File: `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/interface.go`\n  - Interface: `Interface` with `V1alpha1()` accessor\n  - Verify: Group accessor returns version-specific interface\n\n- [ ] **T4.4** Generate version interface\n  - File: `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go`\n  - Interface: `Interface` with `AgentRuntimes()` and `CodeInterpreters()`\n  - Verify: Version accessor returns type-specific informers\n\n- [ ] **T4.5** Generate AgentRuntime informer\n  - File: `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n  - Interface: `AgentRuntimeInformer` with `Informer()` and `Lister()`\n  - Function: `NewAgentRuntimeInformer(factory, namespace, tweakListOptions)`\n  - Function: `NewFilteredAgentRuntimeInformer(factory, namespace, tweakListOptions)`\n  - Verify: Informer returns `cache.SharedIndexInformer`\n\n- [ ] **T4.6** Generate CodeInterpreter informer\n  - File: `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n  - Interface: `CodeInterpreterInformer` with `Informer()` and `Lister()`\n  - Function: `NewCodeInterpreterInformer(...)`\n  - Function: `NewFilteredCodeInterpreterInformer(...)`\n  - Verify: Informer returns `cache.SharedIndexInformer`\n\n- [ ] **T4.7** Generate generic informer\n  - File: `client-go/informers/externalversions/generic.go`\n  - Interface: `GenericInformer` with `Informer()` and `Lister()`\n  - Function: `ForResource(resource)` switches on:\n    - `v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithResource(\"agentruntimes\")`\n    - `v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithResource(\"codeinterpreters\")`\n  - Verify: Generic informer routes to correct type informer\n\n- [ ] **T4.8** Generate internal interfaces\n  - File: `client-go/informers/externalversions/internalinterfaces/factory_interfaces.go`\n  - Type: `NewInformerFunc`\n  - Type: `TweakListOptionsFunc`\n  - Interface: `SharedInformerFactory` (minimal)\n  - Verify: Shared interfaces support factory pattern\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: Lister Generation\n\n- [ ] **T5.1** Generate AgentRuntimeLister\n  - File: `client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n  - Interface: `AgentRuntimeLister` with:\n    - `List(selector) ([]*AgentRuntime, error)`\n    - `AgentRuntimes(namespace) AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister`\n  - Interface: `AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister` with:\n    - `List(selector) ([]*AgentRuntime, error)`\n    - `Get(name) (*AgentRuntime, error)`\n  - Function: `NewAgentRuntimeLister(indexer)`\n  - Verify: Lister uses `cache.Indexer` for read-only access\n\n- [ ] **T5.2** Generate CodeInterpreterLister\n  - File: `client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n  - Interface: `CodeInterpreterLister` with same methods\n  - Interface: `CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister` with same methods\n  - Function: `NewCodeInterpreterLister(indexer)`\n  - Verify: Lister uses correct GroupResource\n\n- [ ] **T5.3** Generate lister expansion interfaces\n  - File: `client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/expansion_generated.go`\n  - Interface: `AgentRuntimeListerExpansion` (empty)\n  - Interface: `AgentRuntimeNamespaceListerExpansion` (empty)\n  - Interface: `CodeInterpreterListerExpansion` (empty)\n  - Interface: `CodeInterpreterNamespaceListerExpansion` (empty)\n  - Verify: Expansion hooks available for custom list/query methods\n\n---\n\n## Phase 6: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **T6.1** Write clientset constructor tests\n  - Test: `TestNewForConfig`\n  - Test: `TestNewForConfigOrDie`\n  - Test: `TestNew`\n  - Verify: Clientset created with correct REST configuration\n\n- [ ] **T6.2** Write typed client CRUD tests\n  - Test: `TestAgentRuntimeCreate` with fake clientset\n  - Test: `TestAgentRuntimeGet`\n  - Test: `TestAgentRuntimeList`\n  - Test: `TestAgentRuntimeUpdate`\n  - Test: `TestAgentRuntimeDelet